<div class="py-5" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-xl:177:37"></div>
<h5 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:1:21">Help Us Raise $2.5&nbsp;million in 2026!</h5>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:4:10"></div>
<div class="row my-3" data-zesty-id="design:columns:2columns:5:79">
<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12" data-zesty-id="design:columns:2columns:5:79-1:2 Columns - Equal:0">
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:2:13">
	We have successfully raised $14&nbsp;million towards our <span style="color:#ed1c2b;"><strong>Rebuilding Hope Restoring Lives </strong></span>shelter renovation project. However, we cannot break ground until we reach our goal of raising the remaining $2.5&nbsp;million. Help us provide a place for Greenville families to get back on their feet. Make a pledge today!
</p>
				</div>
<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12" data-zesty-id="design:columns:2columns:5:79-1:2 Columns - Equal:1">
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:3:69">
	<a href="https://fundraise.givesmart.com/form/SlufyQ?vid=1kddst"><span class="btn btn-solid btn-red">Donate Now</span></a>
</p>
